        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " from the multitude of dead bodies which upon the taking of the city should be slain and thrown into this valley. It was expounded ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "bld",
        "text": "Jeremiah 7:32,33",
        "children": [
          {
